'''Tom Polger''' is a professor in the Department of Philosophy at the [[University of Cincinnati]] in the United States. His research focuses on [[Naturalism (philosophy)|naturalistic]] accounts of the [[metaphysics]] of mind. Polger is a past president of the [[Southern Society for Philosophy and Psychology]].<ref name=SSPP>[http://southernsociety.org/Past.html Past officers]. [[Southern Society for Philosophy and Psychology]]. Retrieved December 27, 2015.</ref>
